data.description: Don't miss your chance to own the largest condo w/ a private ELEVATOR & beautiful wooded views. The dining room features an arched entrance that leads to a spacious great room w/ a cozy fireplace. The flooring in the dining room, great room, sitting room/study, hallway, & storage closet has been upgraded to new luxury vinyl plank. The kitchen is well-equipped & includes a pretty bay window, upgraded white raised panel cabinets, laminate countertops, ceramic tile flooring, & all appliances. The owner's suite is generously sized & comes w/ an adjoining sitting room as well as a HUGE walk-in closet. The ensuite primary bath has a white double bowl vanity, a jetted tub, & a separate shower. Step out onto the covered porch, which has composite decking & can potentially be screened in the future. Updates include new luxury vinyl plank flooring, updated HVAC (2019), & water heater (2021). Enjoy carefree living in a vibrant 55+ community w/ a range of activities, a fitness center, & a pool.
